name: ACYA E-SPORT CENTER DESIGN CHALLENGE (MEMORY TOKEN)
description: IN 2021, ACYA HAD ORGANIZE AN E-SPORTS DESIGN COMPETITION AS PART OF ITS ADVOCACY TOWARDS YOUNG ARCHITECTS IN ASIA TO PROMOTE TECHNOLOGICAL ADOPTION IN THE AREAS OF IOT, BLOCKCHAIN, GAMIFICATION AND SUSTAINABILITY. THE COMPETITION WAS CONVENE BY AR QHAWARIZMI UNDER THE LEADERSHIP OF ACYA CHAIRMAN AR RIDHA RAZAK(MALAYSIA)  AND FINAL JUDGING IN SEPTEMBER WITH THE PRESENCE OF ARCASIA PRESIDENT AR RITA SOH. WE CONGRATULATE ALL WINNERS AND THANK YOU TO ALL SPONSORS.
